### Git Operations
- `git add <files>` - Stage files
- `git status` - Check status
- `git diff` - Show changes
- `git log --oneline` - View commit history
- ‚ùå `git commit` - NEVER auto-commit (user must review)
- ‚ùå `git push` - NEVER auto-push (user must approve)

